# ============================================================================
# TODO checklist (impl réelle) — MAX++
# ============================================================================

# Parser
# - Définir la grammaire .muf (clés, tables, arrays, strings multi-line, escapes).
# - Produire AST MufDocument + spans exacts.
# - Détecter duplicate keys, merges de tables, arrays-of-tables si supportés.

# Decoder (generic)
# - Mapper les sections:
#     * [package], [workspace], [toolchain], [profile.*]
#     * [dependencies], [dependencies.dev], [dependencies.build]
#     * [features], [target.*]
#     * [publish]
# - Type checking strict (TypeMismatch) + UnknownKey.
# - Support conditions cfg/platform (MufCfgExpr / MufPlatform).

# Decoder (cipher)
# - Lire des sections:
#     * [cipher]
#     * [[cipher.module]]
#     * [[cipher.preset]]
#     * [cipher.policy.*]
# - Convertir strings -> enums (alg, family, mode, direction, iv_policy, nonce_policy).
# - Remplir limites par défaut selon (alg/mode).
#
# Validation
# - Cohérence policy:
#     * ECB interdit par défaut (allow_ecb=false)
#     * CBC/ECB: padding valide (None/PKCS7/ISO7816-4, etc.)
#     * CTR/XorStream: nonce/iv policy cohérente
#     * XTS: requires tweak policy (extension future)
# - Streaming:
#     * CTR/XorStream streaming ok
#     * CBC streaming: update multiple of block except finish (padding)
# - Limits:
#     * msg_max, key/iv/nonce bounds
# - Deps/features:
#     * deps existantes, cycles, features inconnues
#
# ABI
# - Impl marshalling struct pour tool/runtime.
# - Diagnostics stable ordering.
#
# Presets
# - Presets standards:
#     * aes_ctr_default
#     * aes_cbc_pkcs7_compat
#     * chacha20_stream_fast
# - Provider overrides + fallback.

.end